<script>
  var currentsponsor = 1;
  var dictofsponsors = { 1: "public/img/sponsor1.svg", 2: "public/img/sponsor2.svg", 3: "public/img/sponsor3.svg", 4: "public/img/sponsor4.svg", 5: "public/img/sponsor5.svg", 6: "public/img/sponsor6.svg", 7: "public/img/sponsor7.svg", 8: "public/img/sponsor8.svg", 9: "public/img/sponsor9.svg", 10: "public/img/sponsor10.svg" };

  function nextsponsor() {
    if (currentsponsor == 10) {
      currentsponsor = 1;
    } else currentsponsor = currentsponsor + 1;
  }

  function image(img) {
    nextsponsor();

    img.src = dictofsponsors[currentsponsor.toString()];
  }
</script>

<Layout title="About">
  <h1>About Sakura Festival</h1>
  <section class="about1">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about1sakura">
        <img src="public/img/about.svg" alt="Sakura træ" />
      </div>
      <div class="text">
        <h2 class="aboutoverskrift">It all started with a Cherry Blossom</h2>
        <p class="abouttext">
          The original idea came from the noble deed of donation of 200 cherry blossom (Sakura) trees by Mr. Seiichi Takaki, President of Andersen Institute of Bread & Life, the holding company of Andersen Group of Hiroshima City, and the employees of the company.
          <br />
          <br /> The donated trees were planted in Langelinie Park. Mr. Takaki is Honorary Consul of Denmark and he was appointed to the honorable position of ambassador of H.C. Andersen on the occasion of the 200th anniversary of H.C. Andersen’s birthday in 2005. The donated Sakura trees were planted in Langelinie Park.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="about2">
    <div class="container2">
      <div class="about2sakura">
        <img src="public/img/aboutbillede.svg" alt="Sakura træ" />
      </div>
      <div class="text">
        <h2 class="aboutoverskrift2">The magic of Sakura trees</h2>
        <p class="abouttext">
          In Japan people love and admire Sakura blossom and almost everybody go out to enjoy its beauty together with families, friends, lovers, office-mates and so forth wherever and whenever Sakura bloom.
          <br />
          <br /> Once a year Sakura connects people and people meet people under Sakura trees. It is also the utmost and fundamental goal of the Committee.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="about3">
    <div class="container3">
      <div class="text">
        <h2 class="aboutoverskrift3">Meet our sponsors</h2>
      </div>
      <section class="sponsorliste">
        <div class="sponsors"></div>
        <img src="public/img/sponsor1.svg" />
        <img src="public/img/sponsor2.svg" />
        <img src="public/img/sponsor3.svg" />
        <img src="public/img/sponsor4.svg" />
        <img src="public/img/sponsor5.svg" />
        <div class="sponsors2"></div>
        <img src="public/img/sponsor6.svg" />
